AreaClass:
navigation area type that will be use when this static mesh is used as
    a navigation obstacle. See bIsDynamicObstacle.
    Empty AreaClass means the default obstacle class will be used
bGatherConvexGeometry: If set, convex collisions will be exported offline for faster runtime navmesh building (increases memory usage)
bCreateOnClient: If false, will not create nav collision when connecting as a client
